  "body": "## Summary\n- Refreshes the committed visual-smoke baseline from the current web export after a runtime run proved the existing PNG hashes were stale.\n- Adds committed-manifest assertions that every route records `firstRunAboutDismissed` and `languagePickerDismissed` booleans from the current RouteCapture schema.\n- Updates the launch-overlay suppression allowlist to match the refreshed browser evidence for onboarding, settings, and chapter route captures.\n\n## Validation\n- `npm run build:web:export -- --max-workers 2`\n- `npm run test:e2e -- tests/e2e/visual-smoke.spec.ts --workers=1` (default temp output)\n- `VISUAL_SMOKE_UPDATE_BASELINE=1 npm run test:e2e -- tests/e2e/visual-smoke.spec.ts --workers=1` (committed baseline refresh)\n- `npm run test:screenshot-manifest`\n- `npm run typecheck -- --pretty false`\n- `npx prettier --check scripts/visual-smoke-report.test.js reports/2026-05-15-uiux-screenshots/manifest.json`\n- `git diff --check`",
